title: Gomier's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Take-out, Caribbean, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small restaurant established since Dec 1997. Offers vegetarian, vegan, and fish. Makes its own soy milk, tofu, and soy sausage and has soy ice cream and whole wheat baked goods. Also offers cooking courses and nutritional consultation. Wi-fi for customers.
